metadata.description: Greg Rucka's fan favorite private eye is back in a new ONGOING series illustrated by Justin Greenwood (Image Comics' THE FUSE)! Things never go according to plan for Dex Parios--it doesn't matter whether it's work or play. When a weekend of soccer fun (both playing and watching!) turns ugly, it's up to Dex to get to the bottom of the violence before a heated rivalry transforms into an all out war!
metadata.name: Stumptown, Vol. 3
